OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FZara starts charging       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fshoppers for online returns
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Fashion giant Zara has become the      
OL,6, latest retailer to charge shoppers who 
OL,7, return items bought online.            
OL,9,FCustomers now must pay #1.95 to return 
OL,10,Fclothes, with the cost taken from their
OL,11,Frefund. Items bought online can still  
OL,12,Fbe returned for free in stores.        
OL,14,FHigh Street firms such as Uniqlo and   
OL,15,FNext already charge for online returns.
OL,17,FOnline shopping boomed in the pandemic,
OL,18,Fbut customers are more likely to return
OL,19,Fitems bought online than in store,     
OL,20,Fraising costs for retailers.           
